			Researchwork
			
			Hisresearchinterestsincludelaserphysics,photoniccrystalsandquantumoptics.Thedetailedcontentsinclude:thetemporaland/orspatialevolutionoflightfieldsthroughdispersivemediaandphotonicbandstructures,thedynamicsofphotonsthroughmulti-layerstructuresandartificialmetamaterials,thecoherenttheoryoflaserbeamsandpulses,andtheinteractionoflightfieldandmulti-levelatoms.

Hetheoreticallyinvestigatedthebandgapof1DPCcontainingthemetamaterials,andstudiedtheGoos-H&auml;ncheneffectindielectricfilms,multi-layeredstructuresandone-dimensionalphotoniccrystals,andalsofocusedonthesuperluminalpropagationofpulsesindifferentmedia.Ontheotherhand,heisalsointerestingintheopticaltweezers.In2009,heproposedtherealizationoftheopticalDiracpointinhomogenousartificialmetamaterials,anddemonstratedtheZitterbewegungeffectandanomalousGoos-H&auml;ncheneffectneartheopticalDiracpoint,andrevealedthequantumpropertiesoftheatomicemissionandtheLambshiftofatwo-levelatomneartheopticalDiracpoint.

Uptonow,hehastotallypublishedmorethan60refereedpapers.Totalother-citationsaremorethan600times.In2007,hewasawardedthesecondclassofNationalUniversityNaturalSciencePrizeofChina.Asaprincipalinvestigator,heperformedtwoNSFCprojectsatZhejiangUniversityandaHongKongRGCprojectattheChineseUniversityofHongKong.
			
				
